                Download Iran Audio Guide application for free and see for yourself<br />
            </p>
        </header>
        <ul class="icons major">
            <li>
                <a ng-click="showPopup('Apple')">
                    <span class="icon fa-apple major style1"></span>
                </a>
            </li>
